"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:104:\"http://wordpress.tv/2011/07/30/andy-crofford-guest-blogging-or-how-to-find-the-best-and-avoid-the-pests/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2535:\"<p>WordCamp Fayetteville &#8211; WordPress Blogger Track, video 02 -</p>\n<p>Guest Blogging: How to find the best and avoid the pests.</p>\n<div>Presented by <strong><a href=\"http://2011.fayetteville.wordcamp.org/speakers-2#andy-crofford\">Andy Crofford</a></strong> • WordPress Blogger Track</div>\n<p>A presentation on finding good/great guest bloggers. This talk includes:</p>\n<p>- What makes a good guest blogger</p>\n<p>- Methods of finding guest bloggers</p>\n<p>Guest blogging is essential for anyone who is serious about running a blog.</p>\n<div id=\"v-KTQPxBBr-1\" class=\"video-player\">\n</div>\n<br />  <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gocomments/wptv.wordpress.com/6734/\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/comments/wptv.wordpress.com/6734/\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/godelicious/wptv.wordpress.com/6734/\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/delicious/wptv.wordpress.com/6734/\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gofacebook/wptv.wordpress.com/6734/\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/facebook/wptv.wordpress.com/6734/\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gotwitter/wptv.wordpress.com/6734/\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/twitter/wptv.wordpress.com/6734/\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gostumble/wptv.wordpress.com/6734/\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/stumble/wptv.wordpress.com/6734/\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"