9:15','',4,'http://localhost:8080/aptana3/wordpress/?p=49',0,'revision','',0),(50,1,'2011-08-18 17:43:46','2011-08-18 09:43:46','上几天总结了如何使用JNI框架，实现Java调用C/C++实现的动态链接库，其实JNI除了能够帮助实现Java调用C/C++还包括用C/C++调用Java，但是像我这种java低端程序娃应该不会苦逼的用C/C++去调用Java玩，所以有需要的同志可以继续专研一下。\r\n\r\n    这里要介绍的是一个在JNI基础上是实现的开源框架JNA，它能够使得Java调用C/C++更加容易使用，它为我们包装了一层，从而不需要我们去考虑如何实现中间的那个DLL，直接调用通用的C/C++的DLL即可。甚至我们不在需要学习很多jstring,jint，等等这些苦逼的数据类型，JNA会自动的实现映射，虽然这些映射大多都是基础的数据类型映射，但是在大多数情况下已经够用了。\r\n\r\n   OK，下面开始介绍JNA。\r\n\r\n一、JNA介绍\r\n\r\nJNA provides Java programs easy access to native shared libraries (DLLs on Windows) without writing anything but Java code—no JNI or native code is required. This functionality is comparable to Windows\' Platform/Invoke and Python\'s ctypes. Access is dynamic at runtime without code generation.\r\n\r\nJNA allows you to call directly into native functions using natural Java method invocation. The Java call looks just like it does in native code. Most calls require no special handling or configuration; no boilerplate or generated code is required.\r\n\r\nJNA的官方介绍，大概的意思就是JNA能够让我们只写java代码，不用考虑任何本地代码就可以实现动态调用的一种框架，大体思想和.NET平台的P/Invoke差不多（不懂的可以自己找找看,应该是.NET平台大概意思就是微软推出的一个可以使得服务跨平台调用的框架）。而且JNA能够让我们使用DLL就像我们使用jar包一样容易。\r\n\r\n二、JNA下载\r\n\r\n大概下载的包jna.jar. platform.jar，你也可以将整个工程都下载回来自己研究下，下载地址为：\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/twall/jna\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n三、HelloJNA，先简单介绍一个小例子，让大家熟悉一下\r\n\r\nimport com.sun.jna.Library;\r\n\r\nimport com.sun.jna.Native;\r\n\r\nimport com.sun.jna.Platform;\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n/** Simple example of native library declaration and usage. */\r\n\r\npublic class HelloWorld {\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n    public interface CLibrary extends Library {\r\n\r\n        CLibrary INSTANCE = (CLibrary)\r\n\r\n            Native.loadLibrary((Platform.isWindows() ? \"msvcrt\" : \"c\"),\r\n\r\n                               CLibrary.class);\r\n\r\n   \r\n\r\n        void printf(String format, Object... args);\r\n\r\n    }\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\r\n\r\n        CLibrary.INSTANCE.printf(\"Hello, JNA/n\");\r\n\r\n        for (int i=0;i < args.length;i++) {\r\n\r\n            CLibrary.INSTANCE.printf(\"Argument %d: %s/n\", i, args[i]);\r\n\r\n        }\r\n\r\n    }\r\n\r\n}\r\n\r\n运行结果为Hello,JNA,\r\n\r\n这个本质上是调用了msvcrt.dll这个的printf方法实现的。（和我一起说，so easy。）\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n四、JNA实现人脸识别调用。\r\n\r\n这就要提到昨天写的人脸识别的那个程序，需要我们将其封装成DLL，以便供java调用，这个dll的规范写法大家可以自己找点资料学习一下，不是很麻烦，我这个很简单。\r\n\r\n源码如下\r\n\r\n1.FaceDetectionJava.h\r\n\r\n#ifdef MYLIBAPI\r\n#else\r\n#define MYLIBAPI extern \"C\" _declspec(dllimport)\r\n#endif\r\n#pragma once\r\n\r\n#pragma comment(lib,\"cv200\")\r\n#pragma comment(lib,\"cxcore200\")\r\n#pragma comment(lib,\"highgui200\")\r\n\r\n\r\nMYLIBAPI typedef struct{\r\n    double x;\r\n    double y;\r\n    double r;\r\n}CIRCLE,*LPSCIRCLE;\r\n\r\nMYLIBAPI void getFaces(LPSCIRCLE lpst,char *filename,int m);\r\n\r\n说明：\r\n\r\n\"#pragma once\"意思在Include头文件的时候有可能各个头文件相互引用，造成重复，标注了这个就会只引入一次。\r\n\r\n#pragma comment(lib,\"cv200\")\r\n#pragma comment(lib,\"cxcore200\")\r\n#pragma comment(lib,\"highgui200\")\r\n\r\n这个的意思就是引入lib文件，在人脸识别的日志有介绍，这三个是OpenCV人脸识别用到的lib文件。0\r\n\r\n“MYLIBAPI”这个关键字是DLL文件暴漏的对外接口必须标注的关键字，如同java包得interface一样，容易理解吧。\r\n\r\nstruct CIRCLE,*LPSCIRCLE是圆的定义，x,y为圆心，r为半径，这个需要在java中写一个对应的Structure类，关于java和C中的各个数据类型的对应关系如下\r\n\r\nJava—C和操作系统数据类型的对应表\r\nJava Type \r\n C Type \r\n Native Representation \r\n \r\nboolean\r\n int\r\n 32-bit integer (customizable)\r\n \r\nbyte\r\n char\r\n 8-bit integer\r\n \r\nchar\r\n wchar_t\r\n platform-dependent\r\n \r\nshort\r\n short\r\n 16-bit integer\r\n \r\nint\r\n int\r\n 32-bit integer\r\n \r\nlong\r\n long long, __int64\r\n 64-bit integer\r\n \r\nfloat\r\n float\r\n 32-bit floating point\r\n \r\ndouble\r\n double\r\n 64-bit floating point\r\n \r\nBuffer \r\nPointer \r\n pointer\r\n platform-dependent (32- or 64-bit pointer to memory)\r\n \r\n<T>[] (array of primitive type)\r\n pointer\r\narray\r\n 32- or 64-bit pointer to memory (argument/return)\r\ncontiguous memory (struct member)\r\n \r\n除了上面的类型，JNA还支持常见的数据类型的映射。\r\n \r\nString \r\n char*\r\n NUL-terminated array (native encoding or jna.encoding)\r\n \r\nWString \r\n wchar_t*\r\n NUL-terminated array (unicode)\r\n \r\nString[] \r\n char**\r\n NULL-terminated array of C strings\r\n \r\nWString[] \r\n wchar_t**\r\n NULL-terminated array of wide C strings\r\n \r\nStructure \r\n struct*\r\nstruct\r\n pointer to struct (argument or return) (or explicitly)\r\nstruct by value (member of struct) (or explicitly)\r\n \r\nUnion \r\n union\r\n same as Structure \r\n \r\nStructure[] \r\n struct[]\r\n array of structs, contiguous in memory\r\n \r\nCallback \r\n <T> (*fp)()\r\n function pointer (Java or native)\r\n \r\nNativeMapped \r\n varies\r\n depends on definition\r\n \r\nNativeLong \r\n long\r\n platform-dependent (32- or 64-bit integer)\r\n \r\nPointerType \r\n pointer\r\n same as Pointer \r\n \r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n然后就是主文件实现，在昨天的基础上修改的\r\n\r\n2.FaceDetectionJava.cpp\r\n\r\n#include \"FaceDetectionJava.h\"\r\n#include \"stdafx.h\"\r\n#include <string>\r\n#include \"cv.h\"\r\n#include \"highgui.h\"\r\n\r\n\r\n#ifdef _DEBUG\r\n#define new DEBUG_NEW\r\n#endif\r\n\r\nusing namespace std;\r\n\r\n\r\nchar* cascade_name2=\"haarcascade_frontalface_alt_tree.xml\";//分类器的名称\r\nCvHaarClassifierCascade* cascade;//特征类分器\r\nCvMemStorage* storage;\r\nIplImage* src;\r\n\r\nvoid getFaces(LPSCIRCLE lpst,char *filename,int m){\r\n\r\n // TODO: 在此添加命令处理程序代码\r\n    CString fileName;\r\n    //打开文件对话窗口\r\n    \r\n    //获得文件名\r\n    fileName = filename;\r\n\r\n    //必要的类型转换\r\n    std::string tempName = (LPCSTR)CStringA(fileName);\r\n    const char* tmp = tempName.c_str();\r\n    //打开文件，若失败则返回]\r\n\r\n   if((src=cvLoadImage(tmp,CV_LOAD_IMAGE_ANYCOLOR))==0)\r\n        return ;\r\n    //加载（分类器层叠）训练库\r\n    cascade = (CvHaarClassifierCascade*)cvLoad( cascade_name2, 0, 0, 0 );\r\n    //加载不成功则显示错误讯息，并退出\r\n    if(cascade)\r\n    {\r\n        storage = cvCreateMemStorage(0);\r\n        \r\n        //如果图片存在则分析并显示结果，否则退出程序\r\n        if(src)\r\n        {\r\n            double scale = 1.3;\r\n            IplImage* gray = cvCreateImage(cvSize(src->width,src->height),8,1);\r\n            IplImage* small_img = cvCreateImage( cvSize( cvRound (src->width/scale),cvRound (src->height/scale)),8,1 );\r\n            int i;\r\n            cvCvtColor( src, gray, CV_BGR2GRAY );\r\n            cvResize( gray, small_img, CV_INTER_LINEAR );\r\n            cvEqualizeHist( small_img, small_img );\r\n            cvClearMemStorage( storage );\r\n            if( cascade )\r\n            {\r\n                //检测人脸\r\n                CvSeq* faces = cvHaarDetectObjects( small_img, cascade, storage, 1.1, 2, 0, cvSize(30, 30) );\r\n                for( i = 0; i < (faces ? faces->total : 0); i++ )\r\n                {\r\n                    \r\n                    CvRect* r = (CvRect*)cvGetSeqElem( faces, i );\r\n                    CvPoint center;\r\n                    int radius;\r\n                    center.x = cvRound((r->x + r->width*0.5)*scale);\r\n                    center.y = cvRound((r->y + r->height*0.5)*scale);\r\n                    radius = cvRound((r->width + r->height)*0.25*scale);\r\n                    if(i==m){\r\n                        lpst->x = center.x;\r\n                        lpst->y = center.y;\r\n                        lpst->r = radius;\r\n                    }\r\n                }\r\n            }\r\n\r\n            cvReleaseImage( &gray );\r\n            cvReleaseImage( &small_img );\r\n        }\r\n        cvReleaseImage(&src);\r\n        cvReleaseMemStorage( &storage );\r\n    }else{\r\n    }\r\n    cvReleaseHaarClassifierCascade( &cascade );\r\n    \r\n};\r\n这里将所有窗口相关的文件代码删除了，而是通过将检测出来的人脸识别出来返回人脸区域的中心位置和半径。\r\n\r\n还有两个include文件是创建DLL工程时候自动生成的 ，应该也是必须的、\r\n\r\n3. stdafx.h\r\n\r\n// stdafx.h : include file for standard system include files,\r\n// or project specific include files that are used frequently,\r\n// but are changed infrequently\r\n\r\n#pragma once\r\n\r\n#ifndef _SECURE_ATL\r\n#define _SECURE_ATL 1\r\n#endif\r\n\r\n#ifndef VC_EXTRALEAN\r\n#define VC_EXTRALEAN            // Exclude rarely-used stuff from Windows headers\r\n#endif\r\n\r\n#include \"targetver.h\"\r\n\r\n#define _ATL_CSTRING_EXPLICIT_CONSTRUCTORS      // some CString constructors will be explicit\r\n\r\n// turns off MFC\'s hiding of some common and often safely ignored warning messages\r\n#define _AFX_ALL_WARNINGS\r\n\r\n#include <afxwin.h>         // MFC core and standard components\r\n#include <afxext.h>         // MFC extensions\r\n\r\n\r\n#include <afxdisp.h>        // MFC Automation classes\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n#ifndef _AFX_NO_OLE_SUPPORT\r\n#include <afxdtctl.h>           // MFC support for Internet Explorer 4 Common Controls\r\n#endif\r\n#ifndef _AFX_NO_AFXCMN_SUPPORT\r\n#include <afxcmn.h>                     // MFC support for Windows Common Controls\r\n#endif // _AFX_NO_AFXCMN_SUPPORT\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n#ifdef _UNICODE\r\n#if defined _M_IX86\r\n#pragma comment(linker,\"/manifestdependency:\\\"type=\'win32\' name=\'Microsoft.Windows.Common-Controls\' version=\'6.0.0.0\' processorArchitecture=\'x86\' publicKeyToken=\'6595b64144ccf1df\' language=\'*\'\\\"\")\r\n#elif defined _M_IA64\r\n#pragma comment(linker,\"/manifestdependency:\\\"type=\'win32\' name=\'Microsoft.Windows.Common-Controls\' version=\'6.0.0.0\' processorArchitecture=\'ia64\' publicKeyToken=\'6595b64144ccf1df\' language=\'*\'\\\"\")\r\n#elif defined _M_X64\r\n#pragma comment(linker,\"/manifestdependency:\\\"type=\'win32\' name=\'Microsoft.Windows.Common-Controls\' version=\'6.0.0.0\' processorArchitecture=\'amd64\' publicKeyToken=\'6595b64144ccf1df\' language=\'*\'\\\"\")\r\n#else\r\n#pragma comment(linker,\"/manifestdependency:\\\"type=\'win32\' name=\'Microsoft.Windows.Common-Controls\' version=\'6.0.0.0\' processorArchitecture=\'*\' publicKeyToken=\'6595b64144ccf1df\' language=\'*\'\\\"\")\r\n#endif\r\n#endif\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n4.targetver.h \r\n#pragma once\r\n\r\n// The following macros define the minimum required platform.  The minimum required platform\r\n// is the earliest version of Windows, Internet Explorer etc. that has the necessary features to run \r\n// your application.  The macros work by enabling all features available on platform versions up to and \r\n// including the version specified.\r\n\r\n// Modify the following defines if you have to target a platform prior to the ones specified below.\r\n// Refer to MSDN for the latest info on corresponding values for different platforms.\r\n#ifndef WINVER                          // Specifies that the minimum required platform is Windows Vista.\r\n#define WINVER 0x0600           // Change this to the appropriate value to target other versions of Windows.\r\n#endif\r\n\r\n#ifndef _WIN32_WINNT            // Specifies that the minimum required platform is Windows Vista.\r\n#define _WIN32_WINNT 0x0600     // Change this to the appropriate value to target other versions of Windows.\r\n#endif\r\n\r\n#ifndef _WIN32_WINDOWS          // Specifies that the minimum required platform is Windows 98.\r\n#define _WIN32_WINDOWS 0x0410 // Change this to the appropriate value to target Windows Me or later.\r\n#endif\r\n\r\n#ifndef _WIN32_IE                       // Specifies that the minimum required platform is Internet Explorer 7.0.\r\n#define _WIN32_IE 0x0700        // Change this to the appropriate value to target other versions of IE.\r\n#endif\r\n\r\n5.编译文件\r\n\r\n这里的编译方法在JNI那篇里面有介绍，就是使用VS2008命令行工具中的CL命令\r\n\r\n \r\n其中命令cl -ID:\\opencv -LD FaceDetectionJava.cpp -Fehello.dll\r\n\r\n其中D:\\opencv是存放的include文件，在opencv安装目录中可以发现\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nFaceDetectionJava.cpp为源文件，hello.dll为生成的dll文件名称。\r\n\r\nOK，hello.dll文件就生成了，\r\n\r\n6.java工程编写\r\n\r\n创建java工程同时将生成的hello.dll放在工程目录下，记住是工程文件夹下第一层，不是放在src或者bin目录下，如\r\n\r\nC:\\Documents and Settings\\Administrator\\workspace\\JNITestJava，下\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nHelloJNA就是要用到的类，源码如下\r\n\r\nimport java.util.ArrayList;\r\n\r\nimport com.sun.jna.Library;\r\nimport com.sun.jna.Native;\r\nimport com.sun.jna.Structure;\r\n\r\n\r\npublic class HelloJNA {\r\n\r\n    \r\n    public interface Hello extends Library {\r\n        /**\r\n         * 当前路径是在项目下，而不是bin输出目录下。\r\n         */\r\n        \r\n        public static class CIRCLE extends Structure{\r\n            public double x;\r\n            public double y;\r\n            public double r;\r\n            \r\n        }\r\n        Hello INSTANCE = (Hello)Native.loadLibrary(\"hello\", Hello.class);\r\n        public void getFaces(CIRCLE c,String s,int i);\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    /**\r\n     * @param args\r\n     */\r\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\r\n        // TODO Auto-generated method stub\r\n\r\n        ArrayList<Hello.CIRCLE> list = new ArrayList<Hello.CIRCLE>();\r\n        String path = \"C:\\\\Documents and Settings\\\\Administrator\\\\My Documents\\\\2.jpg\";\r\n        double rd = 0;\r\n        int i = 0;\r\n        do{\r\n            \r\n            Hello.CIRCLE c = new Hello.CIRCLE();\r\n            Hello.INSTANCE.getFaces(c,path,i);\r\n            rd = c.r;\r\n            if(rd!=0){\r\n                list.add(c);\r\n                System.out.println(c.x);\r\n                System.out.println(c.y);\r\n                System.out.println(c.r);\r\n            }\r\n            i++;\r\n        }while(rd!=0);\r\n\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n说明：class CIRCLE继承了Structure对应的是C++种的struct，这里需要注意的是，里面的变量顺序是一一对应的，不能颠倒的。、\r\n\r\n运行过程中打印出所有的人脸区域数据\r\n\r\n294.0\r\n593.0\r\n55.0\r\n293.0\r\n341.0\r\n175.0\r\n识别出了两张人脸。\r\n\r\n注意，因为没有找到struct[]的好的实现方法，我尝试很多次没有成功，所以只能一个人脸一个人脸的返回，如果有哪位大神做出来希望能够教教我，谢谢啊。\r\n\r\n','（用java调用C第二季）JNA(基于JNI的java调用C程序DLL的易用型框架)简介以及用JNA结合上篇日志人脸识别实现的java调用版总结','','inherit','open','open','','20-revision-2','','','2011-08-18 17:43:46','2011-08-18 09:43:46','',20,'http://localhost:8080/aptana3/wordpress/?p=50',0,'revision','',0),(51,1,'2011-08-19 17:48:02','2011-08-19 09:48:02','12345','12345','','inherit','open','open','','24-revision-4','','','2011-08-19 17:48:02','2011-08-19 09:48:02','',24,'http://localhost:8080/aptana3/wordpress/?p=51',0,'revision','',0),(52,1,'2011-08-18 17:46:28','2011-08-18 09:46:28','想必很多白羊总是抱怨自己常常说错话，因为他们有着单纯爽朗的神经，往往说过了才会懊悔，尽管下定决心要努力学会迂回的艺术，但是单纯直接的白羊，却总感到绕上千肠百转实在是相当吃力,其实这也没有什么关系,白羊的可爱正在于他们的简单直接.。这个正是白羊的魅力所在。单纯可爱。 \r\n','白羊','','inherit','open','open','','22-revision-2','','','2011-08-18 17:46:28','2011-08-18 09:46:28','',22,'http://localhost:8080/aptana3/wordpress/?p=52',0,'revision','',0),(53,1,'2011-08-19 17:48:49','2011-08-19 09:48:49','想必很多白羊总是抱怨自己常常说错话，因为他们有着单纯爽朗的神经，往往说过了才会懊悔，尽管下定决心要努力学会迂回的艺术，但是单纯直接的白羊，却总感到绕上千肠百转实在是相当吃力,其实这也没有什么关系,白羊的可爱正在于他们的简单直接.。这个正是白羊的魅力所在。单纯可爱。 \r\n','白羊','','inherit','open','open','','22-revision-3','','','2011-08-19 17:48:49','2011-08-19 09:48:49','',22,'http://localhost:8080/aptana3/wordpress/?p=53',0,'revision','',0),(54,1,'2011-08-19 16:46:10','2011-08-19 08:46:10','<a href=\"http://localhost:8080/aptana3/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/p_large_vngX_3afe0008fc065c71_副本.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/aptana3/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/p_large_vngX_3afe0008fc065c71_副本.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"p_large_vngX_3afe0008fc065c71_副本\" width=\"720\" height=\"405\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-39\" /></a>','','','inherit','open','open','','40-revision','','','2011-08-19 16:46:10','2011-08-19 08:46:10','',40,'http://localhost:8080/aptana3/wordpress/?p=54',0,'revision','',0),(55,1,'2011-08-19 17:48:16','2011-08-19 09:48:16','aegiryy','Hello','','inherit','open','open','','30-revision-4','','','2011-08-19 17:48:16','2011-08-19 09:48:16','',30,'http://localhost:8080/aptana3/wordpress/?p=55',0,'revision','',0),(56,1,'2011-08-19 15:48:52','2011-08-19 07:48:52','google\r\n摩托罗拉','TEST','','inherit','open','open','','28-revision-3','','','2011-08-19 15:48:52','2011-08-19 07:48:52','',28,'http://localhost:8080/aptana3/wordpress/?p=56',0,'revision','',0),(57,1,'2011-08-18 17:56:02','2011-08-18 09:56:02','love alice forever','ohohoh','','inherit','open','open',